sentences: Sultan Karimov (Kazakh: Сұлтан Кәрімов, Sultan Kárimov), (born 13 September 1993) better known by his stage name Farleon, is a Kazakh electronic musician, record producer, remixer and DJ.
In 2016, his single "Tell Me" caught an eye of Don Diablo, who subsequently signed his collaboration with Dropgun "Fever" to Hexagon.
